Class DeviceSensorsAsyncData

java.lang.Object
  DeviceMessage
      orbotix.robot.base.DeviceAsyncData
          orbotix.robot.base.DeviceSensorsAsyncData

public class DeviceSensorsAsyncData
extends DeviceAsyncData

Client code can receive sensor data from a Sphero by sending a SetDataStreamingCommand to initiate and configure the streaming of sensor data. This class is created by the framework to contain the data returned asynchronously. Client code will need to register a listener with DeviceMessenger which handles dispatching DeviceSensorsAsyncData objects before initiating data streaming.

See Also:
SetDataStreamingCommand, DeviceMessenger
